duties_responsibilities.duty: Coordinate technical teams for client onboarding and technical integrations.
Operationalize data maintenance support models and improve data quality.
Develop ongoing outcomes reports and use data to tell meaningful and actionable stories to client partners.
Partner with the enrollment team and scrub data, drive enrollment strategy.
Troubleshoot and plan course of action for resolution of customer-reported technical issues.
Oversee database configuration, definition of data requirements, and sFTP exchange process for timely launch.
Create and apply SOPs and workflows for successful onboarding of eligibility data.
Create and run adhoc reports, graphs, and various data analysis.

education_certification.credential: BS/BA + 2-5 years work experience in technical analysis at a digital health, healthcare, wellness, benefits, or SaaS company.
